AddressInfo.Title: San Marcos Supercharger
AddressInfo.AccessComments: From I-35N :  Take exit 200 toward Centerpoint Rd;  Merge onto N Interstate 35 Frontage Rd;  Turn right onto Centerpoint Rd;  Continue past main entrance;  Turn left into driveway after VF outlet store;  Continue for 1/4 mile;  Supercharger will be on the right.  /   From I-35S : Take exit 200 toward Centerpoint Rd; Merge onto N Interstate 35 Frontage Rd;  Slight right to stay on N Interstate 35 Frontage Rd;  Turn left onto Centerpoint Rd;  Continue past main entrance;  Turn left into driveway after VF outlet store;  Continue for 1/4 mile;  Supercharger will be on the right.
